Fatty goodiness melting in your mouth, with a potato puree  and a small amount of jus de veau (broth).
So small, yet it will take you a half an hour to finish it because you will just want to savor it again and again.
http://www.yelp.com/biz_photos/0q_BHpxbikVtPRRLRu-U0g?select=HC4f8kFjLVsaWpKzdR8g1A  For the next dish, I substituted the Foie Gras and went with their sauteed ruby red shrimp.
