This was one of them.
Everything was perfect, except the price.
However, I prepared for the hit... though I still cry a little everything when I look at my bank account.
Anyways, if you're looking for a fine dining splurge, this is definitely not a bad choice.
The fountains at the Bellagio are also phenomenal during dinner.

