BEING SORT OF A NARCISSIST, I STARTED WRITING A MEMOIR...  CHAPTER 3:   WHAT I LEARNED IN JUNIOR HIGH Inspired after reading about Pablo Picasso's legendary ways with women, I drew a beautiful pastel of a girl I had a crush on.
