With all of the restaurants to pick from in Las Vegas, we used the Yelp reviews to pick Picasso.
We decided to sit outside since we had reservations on 7/4, just a little before the different hotels had their fireworks.
The service was excellent, we had a great view of the Bellagio's fountain display, and did get to hear some of the fireworks.
Around the time the fireworks were going to start on the side we could actually see, Mother Nature decided it wasn't meant to be.
The rain started and we were then moved inside.
All went quite smoothly considering.
